{"tid":2008911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對家：統一戰線 vs 我哋：內耗分化","createTime":"2020-05-09T11:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T14:08:18.000Z","uid":101392,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a2c46b9bc1c7e72ab9ed53457bce6b672abd78dd","tid":2008911,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:10:51.000Z","msg":"沈旭暉呢兩段片有講，共產黨最擅長係<br />\n「統一戰線」、<br />\n「連結次要敵人，打倒主要敵人」、<br />\n「拉攏大多數人 孤立少數敵人」<br />\n而家「再出發大聯盟」就係做緊呢D嘢<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cqMX7UyXZRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcqMX7UyXZRg&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=c5e3e354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cqMX7UyXZRg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sP-HGiwbTBo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsP-HGiwbTBo&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=1192497d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sP-HGiwbTBo</a><br />\n<br />\n當年國共兩次合作、中共建政後初年連結「民族資產階級」榮毅仁、八大民主黨派、政協都係做緊呢樣嘢<br />\n<br />\n最近「再出發大聯盟」，連佢地口中鬧嘅「曱甴王李嘉誠」、「暴徒校長」段崇智、「黃媒」ViuTV老闆李澤楷都俾佢哋拉入去聯盟入面，就係做緊呢樣嘢，想拉攏大多數中嘅次要敵人、不斷被分化主要敵人、孤立主要敵人，想我哋由多數派變少數派<br />\n<br />\n最近內會俾共狗衝擊，泛民係有改善空間、好多不足，我哋要鞭策、批評都係必須，但係小心長遠唔好進一步將我哋呢邊分化、化整為零，成為少數派<br />\n<br />\n你當泛民係敵人都好，佢地係次要敵人、要連結佢地對付主要敵人<br />\n對家口中「曱甴王」都可以拉埋一條船，我哋唔可以再分化"},{"pid":"bfd2669c4f1efeb04f192dc04dda542d3d1f0470","tid":2008911,"uid":101392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5HiBh0N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5HiBh0N.jpg&h=768c7ef9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n梁振英一方面喺度連結次要敵人 <br />\n拉攏李嘉誠、段崇智<br />\n一方面就想分化我哋 將我哋呢邊化整為零 返去2014之後捉鬼、互屌收場<br />\n泛民本土明明已經可以一齊傾 協調初選<br />\n佢喺度意圖挑起事端 想分化黃營<br />\n李傲然 劉小麗棄選 票源會集中返去本土自決嘅張崑陽 劉澤鋒等<br />\n余德寶棄選 票源會集中去前公民黨毛孟靜 年輕泛民何啟明<br />\n其實係不利黃碧雲出線<br />\n689調返轉嚟講都有連登仔落搭"},{"pid":"ed4c63dbea169ea980df9a371a0f6962cb6abf4e","tid":2008911,"uid":101392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:21:20.000Z","msg":"我哋要做嘅 <br />\n除左制度內泛民本土繼續協調初選之外<br />\n制度外要重啓抗爭 繼續和勇不分 不割蓆 不分化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7513de32928620b6d8d694ab8811680c07d80b9c","tid":2008911,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:21:49.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4nzUThz8BvI&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=b1369174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4nzUThz8BvI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC7YbpoujZlw&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=50057783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw</a>"},{"pid":"fdd9452e87d55140a472b6eb973307aea87dcf68","tid":2008911,"uid":6041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:22:13.000Z","msg":"成日都fb ig都見到班fd日日都係笑鳩泛民<br />\n我更加確信 香港人係唔識玩政治既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連主要同次要既敵人都唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2db7699af0f511a4bb9d956dc15ce3c726c774","tid":2008911,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90b9e6621b05db798fa384c5fd178cb1c7f1dd3","tid":2008911,"uid":1631,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fdd9452e87d55140a472b6eb973307aea87dcf68","tid":2008911,"uid":6041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T11:22:13.000Z","msg":"成日都fb ig都見到班fd日日都係笑鳩泛民<br />\n我更加確信 香港人係唔識玩政治既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連主要同次要既敵人都唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":